Bibloteca For TWU homework

=====================================================================================================
you can download the whole repo, enetr the root directory, then run the commadn below to run apps:

java -cp out/production/Biblioteca/ Biblioteca   (you can just copy that and run it in the root directory)

======================================================================================================

right now, you can only input several command by the output instruction.

That homework is still working in progress.

====================================================================
update at 2012-9-22

Add login fucntionality in library.
Now I currently hard code four users in system,you can use the 
following name to login:
eva, nikita, blair, damon, penny and password are "user" for all.

Once you have logged in, you don't need to type name and password again.
command 3 can list all the books reserved for user.

you may test whatever you like~
Example:
=====================================================================
please input the number:
2
Please log in first!!
please input your name:
eva
please input your password:
user
Please Input Book Name:
JAVA
Thank You! Enjoy the book.
please input command number:
3
All book reserved for you:
JAVA	1	Author1	publisherB
-----------------------------------------------
please input command number:
please input the command number:
3
Please log in first!!
please input your name:
eva
please input your password:
user
You have no book reserved.you may input 2 command to reserve new book!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------





